	<div id="rules">
	<h2>Rules and Instructions</h2>
	
	<h3>Players VS Player</h3>
	<ol>
	<li>Player 1 plays with X and player 2 plays with O</li>
	<li>Winner gets +10 points and the loser gets -10. In case of a draw, both get zero</li>
	<li>Each player is given 10 sec to make his/her move. On exceeding the time limit a random move is made.</li></ol>
	<h3>Players VS Computer</h3>
	<ol>
	<li>Player plays with X and makes the first move.</li>
	<li>Win: +20 points<br>Lose: -5 points<br>Draw: 0 points</li>
	
	<li>Player is given 10 sec to make his/her move. On exceeding the time limit a random move is made.</li></ol>
	</div>
